*Privacy Policy*

1. *Information Collection*: Pink may collect personal information such as name, email address, shipping address, and payment information for the purpose of providing services offered by the Application. Pink may also collect non-personal information such as device information and usage data.

2. *Use of Information*: Personal information collected by Pink may be used for the following purposes:
   a. To process transactions;
   b. To personalize user experience;
   c. To improve customer service;
   d. To send periodic emails regarding orders and other relevant information.

3. *Data Security*: Pink implements a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of personal information. All sensitive information provided is encrypted and transmitted via Secure Socket Layer (SSL) technology.

4. *Disclosure to Third Parties*: Pink does not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer personal information to outside parties unless necessary for the provision of services. This may include trusted third parties who assist in operating the Application or conducting business, as long as they agree to keep this information confidential.

5. *Consent*: By using the Application, you consent to the collection and use of personal information as outlined in this Privacy Policy.

6. *Changes to Privacy Policy*: Pink reserves the right to update or change its Privacy Policy at any time. Users will be notified of any changes to the Privacy Policy on this page.

7. *Contact Information*: If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, you may contact Pink using the information provided on the Application
